OL,4,Cturf war, murder trial told
OL,6,FJoshua Gordon, 27; Melissa Quailey-
OL,7,FDashper, 40; Kristina Ginova, 21; and
OL,8,FTony Porter, 68; all from
OL,9,FLeicestershire, are accused of murder
OL,10,Fand participation in the activities of
OL,11,Fan organised crime group.
OL,13,FMarcus Huntley, 21; and Jordan Mills-
OL,14,FSmith, 33; from Cardiff, are accused
OL,15,Fof murder. The pair previously pleaded
OL,16,Fguilty to participation in the
OL,17,Factivities of an organised crime group.
