OL,3,CWoman shot dead as part of drug gang
OL,4,Cturf war, murder trial told
OL,6,FOpening the case for the prosecution,
OL,7,FJonathan Rees KC said that the
OL,8,Fbackground to the shooting had been
OL,9,Fthe "clash of two organised crime
OL,10,Fgroups."
OL,12,FOne group was headed by Joshua Gordon
OL,13,Fand known as the "Rico OCG", the other
OL,14,Fheaded by Daniel - or "Jimmy" - Joseph.
OL,16,F"Gordon, also known as Rico or Reece,
OL,17,Fwas involved, with his girlfriend,
OL,18,FGinova, in serious drug trafficking,"
OL,19,FMr Rees said.
