OL,6,F"The expansion of Gordon's activities
OL,7,Finto South Wales ` Talbot Green in
OL,8,Fparticular - had not been taken well
OL,9,Fby a rival group of drug dealers, led
OL,10,Fby Daniel Joseph (also known as
OL,11,F"Jimmy"), who were already operating
OL,12,Fin the area."
OL,14,FMr Rees told the jury that members of
OL,15,FJoseph's gang had "twice confronted,
OL,16,Fand humiliated" members of the Rico
OL,17,Fgang in the weeks leading up to the
OL,18,Fshooting.
