OL,3,CWoman shot dead as part of drug gang
OL,4,Cturf war, murder trial told
OL,6,FOn around February 21st/22nd, the
OL,7,Fcourt heard a car carrying Marcus
OL,8,FHuntley was rammed by a 4x4 vehicle
OL,9,Fafter he'd been forced to flee the
OL,10,FTalbot Green property where Joanne
OL,11,FPenney was later shot after being
OL,12,Fcaught dealing drugs. On March 7th
OL,13,Fanother man associated with the Rico
OL,14,Fgroup was "interrogated" and assaulted
OL,15,Fby the rival gang, Mr Rees said.
OL,17,FTwo days later, the court heard,
OL,18,FGordon, Ginova, Porter and Quailey-
OL,19,FDashper travelled from Leicester in a
OL,20,Ftwo-car convoy.
