OL,6,FThree of the defendants, joined by
OL,7,FHuntley and Mills-Smith, then drove to
OL,8,FTalbot Green in Porter's Nissan Note
OL,9,Fvehicle.
OL,11,FIt's claimed Ginova traveled
OL,12,Fseparately to a McDonald's restaurant
OL,13,Fin Cardiff Gate, carrying Gordon's
OL,14,Fphone.
OL,16,FThere, the jury were told, she bought
OL,17,Fa meal for two, and "ensured that
OL,18,FGordon's phone continued to activate
OL,19,Fcell sites in the Pentwyn area of
OL,20,FCardiff."
