OL,6,F"In fact", said Mr Rees, "Gordon was
OL,7,Fwaiting in the car with Porter in
OL,8,FTalbot Green, while Huntley, Mills-
OL,9,FSmith and Quailey-Dashper walked up to
OL,10,Fthe front door of 10 Llys Illtyd to
OL,11,Fcarry out the ambush.
OL,13,F"Quailey-Dashper knocked the front
OL,14,Fdoor then retreated while Huntley, who
OL,15,Fwas standing next to Mills-Smith,
OL,16,Fleant forward and immediately shot at
OL,17,Fthe person who opened the door.
