OL,4,Cturf war, murder trial told
OL,6,F"The initial account gleaned by the
OL,7,Fpolice was that there was a knock at
OL,8,Fthe door, Ms Penney opened the door, a
OL,9,Fgunshot was heard, and Ms Penney came
OL,10,Fback into the living room and stated
OL,11,Fthat she had been shot before
OL,12,Fcollapsing on the floor."
OL,14,FThe court was told that emergency
OL,15,Fworkers tried to save Ms Penney's
OL,16,Flife, performing CPR and a
OL,17,F"resuscitative (clamshell)
OL,18,Fthoracotomy", which revealed a bullet
OL,19,Fhole in Ms Penney's heart.
OL,21,FShe was pronounced dead at the scene.
